Compile with

    mvn package

Run with

    $SPARK_HOME/bin/spark-submit \
    --class com.oreilly.learningsparkexamples.mini.java.WordCount \
    ./build/learning-spark-mini-example-1.0.jar \
    ./WordCount.java ./wordcounts

Here `WordCount.java` is the file on which we want to count the words and
`./wordocunts` is the output path for the wordcounts.
